{
  "stem": "5261.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was sent to the forced camp in [INAUDIBLE], in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wrote-- on the begin when the post was going rather in good way, I received some letter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have probably even in Warsaw one picture of him, and he wrote me-- be carefully.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stay so long as you can because this work condition, what we have here, is so terrible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have to wear our P, as a Polish, on this place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we are treated so bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't go ever-- only work, work, and work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe he is alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he would be not agreed that I have mentioned his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, first I had to ask him in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I give only Hendrik M.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The M is the other name, yeah?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If he-- if I knew that he's no more alive, I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was in my age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I am alive, maybe he is also alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, they-- when I had this good job, it was rather a good job because it was-- [? couldn't pay-- ?] it was joined with the food because the money-- reichsmark-- this was nothing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even-- I have received probably five mark, reichsmark, by this baker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was enough because I couldn't go to see the cinemas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were cinemas for German people only.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't go to the theatre.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Theatre was-- as I told you, I liked music very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was boring time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You must understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was 14 years boy, and I expected something more from [INAUDIBLE], not only darkness in the city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to stay home from 8 o'clock evening until the morning 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Let's say it was summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To go to the bed at 8, it was too early.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
